<h2><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/index.php?id=1296" title="Parkside Candies"> Parkside Candies</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


     

  	<p>Parkside Candies on Main Street in Buffalo, New York, is quite a treat&#8212; food-wise and architecturally. It&#8217;s up in the university district.</p>

	<p>(click on images for larger photo)</p>

	<p><ul class="lightbox"><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/406.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/406t.jpg" alt="" /></a><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/408.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/408t.jpg" alt="" /></a><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/412.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/412t.jpg" alt="" /></a><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/418.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/418t.jpg" alt="buffalo---79.jpg" /></a><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/419.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/419t.jpg" alt="buffalo---80.jpg" /></a><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/420.jpg" rel="lightbox[2]" title=""><img src="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/images/420t.jpg" alt="buffalo---81.jpg" /></a></ul></p>
