<h2><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/index.php?id=1295" title="Buffalo Botanical Gardens"> Buffalo Botanical Gardens</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


        
	<p>My mom is a horticulture volunteer and docent at the <a href="http://www.buffalogardens.com/">Buffalo Botanical Gardens</a>. While we visited her last week in Buffalo she gave us the grand tour!</p>

	<p>The Bot as it&#8217;s affectionately called is an absolute gem. </p>

	<p>(click image to see the gallery)</p>

	<p><a href="/?id=1295"><img src="/images/366t.jpg" title="last-day-vacation---017.jpg" alt="last-day-vacation---017.jpg" width="180" height="135" /></a></p>

