<h2><a href="http://www.ontheriversedge.com/index.php?id=1256" title="2004 Trip to Buffalo-Niagara Falls"> 2004 Trip to Buffalo-Niagara Falls</a></h2>

<div class="entry">


        
	<p>We used to have our photos on a different server and I&#8217;m slowly moving them over. Here is the first batch, recapturing our pre-grad school vacation to Buffalo, Niagara Falls and Niagara-on-the-Lake. I&#8217;ll add captions soon&#8230; </p>

	<p>We plan to go back to the area this spring/summer. I&#8217;m thinking summer as the farmer&#8217;s markets open in July. But I also haven&#8217;t visited my mom there since 2004 so maybe spring. </p>

	<p>(click on images for image gallery)</p>

	<p><a href="/?id=1256"><img src="/images/194.jpg" alt="Niagara Falls" style="width:340px" /></a></p>

